* AUTONEXT >>> Automatic advance logic                                *
*	       entry : Selected client and marker                         *
*				   MRK_SPOT                                           *
*                  O_MRK_NBR                                          *
*                  O_SCHD_PTR                                         *
*        		   O_STP_PTR                                          *
